<div class="row wrapper border-bottom white-bg page-heading">
    <div class="col-lg-10">
        <h2>쿠폰현황</h2>
        <ol class="breadcrumb">
        <li>
            <a href="#">Home</a>
        </li>
        <li>
            <a>Users</a>
        </li>
        <li class="active">
            <strong>쿠폰발급현황</strong>
        </li>
        </ol>
    </div>
</div>
<div class="wrapper wrapper-content animated fadeInRight">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-lg-12">
            <div class="ibox float-e-margins">
                <div class="ibox-content" style="padding-bottom: 10px;">
                    <h3 class="text-navy">쿠폰발급</h3> 
                    <h5>무료 음료쿠폰을 발급하고 싶을 땐, 할인금액에 가장 비싼 음료의 가격을 적으면 됩니다.</h5>
                    <h5>쿠폰 발행갯수 : 한 사람에게 같은 쿠폰을 몇 장 발급할 것인지 설정</h5>
                    <form class="form-horizontal" action="/users/update_coupon/<%= @coupon.id %>" method="GET">
                        <div class="form-group" style="margin-bottom: 0px;">
                            <div class="row">
                                <label class="col-lg-1 control-label" style="text-align:center;">쿠폰명 |</label>
                                <div class="col-lg-2" style="padding-right: 0px;">
                                    <input type="text" class="form-control" name="c_name" value="<%= @coupon.c_name %>" placeholder="ex) 3월 생일자 쿠폰" required="">
                                </div>
                                <label class="col-lg-2 control-label" style="text-align:center;">쿠폰발행갯수 |</label>
                                <div class="col-lg-1" style="padding-right: 0px;">
                                    <input type="number" class="form-control" value="<%= @coupon.unit %>" name="unit" required="">
                                </div>
                                <label class="col-lg-2 control-label" style="text-align:center;">할인금액 |</label>
                                <div class="col-lg-2" style="padding-right: 0px;">
                                    <input type="number" class="form-control" name="price" value="<%= @coupon.price %>" required="">
                                </div>
                                <div class="col-lg-1" style="padding-right: 0px;">
                                    <button class="btn btn-warning btn-block">등록</button>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="row" style="margin-top: 20px;">
                                <label class="col-lg-1 control-label" style="text-align:center;">내용 |</label>
                                <div class="col-lg-9" style="padding-right: 0px;">
                                    <textarea class="form-control" name="content" placeholder="255자 이내로 작성해주세요" rows="5"><%= @coupon.content %></textarea>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </form>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<% content_for :javascript do %>

